### Azure OpenAI (keep real values in .env; never commit secrets)
#
# In Azure OpenAI, the "model" parameter is typically your DEPLOYMENT NAME.
# If your deployment is named "gpt-4o-mini", keep it as-is.
AZURE_OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://greatcodeoff.openai.azure.com/
AZURE_OPENAI_KEY=<YOUR_AZURE_OPENAI_KEY>
AZURE_API_VERSION=2025-01-01-preview

### Chatbot settings
# Set to 1 to enable AI-wrapped (open-ended) responses
CHATBOT_USE_AI=1
